section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') PLANNING FEATURE FOR GLOBALEUR
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      Planning is the primary feature for Globaleur App.
      The whole feature is very complicated.
      However, we used to use one page to operate all functions.
      After user testing, we figured out that users felt so confused about our planning page.
      The redesign of the planning page is essential to help increase engagement when users browse and organize their trips.

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') MY ROLE
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      My responsibilities included UX research, UX design,
      interactive prototyping, visual design.
      I collaborated with other designers, PMs, researchers, and developers.

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') PROBLEM
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      We used to combine all the functions into the same page(Editing, daily details, map, day tabs, add new places, etc.).
      The planning page is very complicated for users to use.
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      The users who did the user testing were unfamiliar with our app.
      Some users ended up in the wrong category,
      which could diminish their confidence with our platform.
      Some users did not have the patience to figure out what does this page used.
      It was likely that this page contained so much information that users might feel lost and confused,
      then they ended up leaving our site entirely.
      Some users did not care what the contents were,
      which lead to another problem: how to attract users' eyes and display more valuable materials on the page.
    div(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10')
      ol(class='number-list')
        li
          p.
            Too many functions displayed on one page.
            It is too complicated for one app page to show that much information.
        li
          p.
            Contents need to be more careful to reveal on the page.
            Pure text leaves so much white space, which looks too simple to dull.

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') SOLUTION
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      Redesign the process of planning pages can increase users' potential for discovery,
      editing, and engagement with the app.
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10 solution-subtitle').
      It will be achieved through 2 goals:
    div(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10')
      ol(class='number-list')
        li
          p.
            Users would not feel lost and confused,
            and there is no need to spend more time to learn while they are planning the trips.
        li
          p.
            Leverage the content and Increase the click rate for users to check the suggestions.

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') PROCESS
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      I follow an end-to-end design process that starts with research and continues with product thinking,
      wireframe, user testing, design refinement, visual design, and post-launch support.
    div(class='section-img-process section-img col-lg-12 container-fluid')
      div(class='section-img-process row justify-content-md-center')
        div(class='col-lg-10 ver-hor-center')
          img(src="/public/assets/PF_process.png", alt="")

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') DESIGN TENETS
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      The two tenets were the guideline while I was designing the flows.
    h3(class='section-sub-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') Discoverability
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      A.I. trip suggestion is one of the most prominent advantages of our platform.
      Users should be aware of live event offerings,
      famous POI(Point of Interest) suggestions,
      and viewing availability across multiple platforms.
    h3(class='section-sub-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') Balance
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
      There must be a balance between giving the user too much and too little information.
      Too much, we risk overwhelming the user and complicating the process.
      Too little, we risk confusing them.

section(class="container-fluid")
  div(class="section-wrapper row justify-content-md-center")
    h2(class='section-title col-lg-8 col-md-10') COMPETITORS
    p(class='col-lg-8 col-md-10').
